      <title><![CDATA[Welcome]]></title>
        <descriptionText><![CDATA[<Introtext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; color:#cc0033; margin:10px; padding:0 0 0 5px; background:#e8e8e8; border-bottom:1px solid #333; display:block;">Welcome</Introtext><welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">Welcome to the <b> OAPI Sales Accelerator Simulation.</b><br>In this third round of the simulation, you use the skills you have acquired to engage your customer at Maycomb Community Hospital and practice what you have learned in the session.<BR><BR>This round of the simulation will include six decisions, and you will have 30 minutes to complete the simulation. Each of the possible questions you consider has been rated according to the following individual metrics, so your score will reflect whether your decision making is in line with these characteristics:<BR><BR><b>Scoring Metrics:</b><BR><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; padding-left:20px;">Customerâ€™s Goals</span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions will help your customer better understand their desired patient treatment goals for<span style="margin:0 0 0 15px;"> patients with hyponatremia</span></li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions will capture new opportunities for the customer</li><br><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold;padding-left:20px;">Sales Progress</span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;padding-left:20px;">Decisions build on previous discussions and align with where the customer is in their<span style="margin:0 0 0 15px;"> prescribing cycle</span></li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions advance the sale by "closing" at multiple points in the prescribing cycle</li><BR><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold;padding-left:20px;">Trusted Advisor Relationship </span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions demonstrate a deep understanding of the customer's priorities and goals</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc; padding-left:20px;">Decisions genuinely engage the customer by partnering with the customer to create value</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:none;"><BR>Note: This simulation includes discussion on patient treatment goals including patient satisfaction.  We have no patient satisfaction data for our product.</li><BR></welcomeText><lasttext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; color:#000; background-color:#c0c0c0; margin:10px; padding:2px 0 2px 5px; display:block;"><i>Please tap <b>Continue</b> or swipe to see information about you and your customer.</i></lasttext><welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><BR><BR><I><B>Simulation Version: January 2012   0711T-3576C</B></I></welcomeText>]]></descriptionText>
